The '''Wild Plum''' is a [[Fruits|fruit]] found via [[foraging]] throughout Stardew Valley in the [[Fall]].  It can also be grown from [[Fall Seeds]] and can be found at any time (randomly) in the [[The Cave|Farm Cave]] if the fruit bat option is chosen.

==Gifting==
